BUS CONTRACT: Same SPI bus. YOUR RECORD TYPE: satisfied. Data schema: {next_signal: halt}

STATE: {{state}}

Return ONLY JSON: {"record_type":"satisfied","data":{"next_signal":"halt"},"reasoning":"Goal complete or honest give-up."}
